1
00:00:11,538 --> 00:00:15,941
<i>Hey boys, listen up!</i>

2
00:00:16,009 --> 00:00:20,537
<i>Humans aren't such a big deal</i>

3
00:00:21,247 --> 00:00:25,377
<i>Who needs tomorrow anyway,</i>

4
00:00:25,452 --> 00:00:28,649
<i>so don't hide your fists</i>

5
00:00:30,590 --> 00:00:32,854
<i>You're not old enough</i>

6
00:00:32,926 --> 00:00:39,229
<i>to sell your dreams away to uncertainty</i>

7
00:00:40,166 --> 00:00:44,603
<i>Hey boys, you're the only ones</i>

8
00:00:44,671 --> 00:00:48,198
<i>who can pull the trigger in your heart</i>

9
00:00:49,642 --> 00:00:51,576
<i>All the kids said</i>

10
00:00:51,644 --> 00:00:54,579
<i>We're living in this senseless, ridiculous,</i>

11
00:00:54,647 --> 00:00:58,947
<i>awesome world right at this moment,</i>

12
00:00:59,152 --> 00:01:01,416
<i>All the kids said</i>

13
00:01:01,488 --> 00:01:07,290
<i>Don't forget every truth or lie</i>

14
00:01:08,695 --> 00:01:11,031
<i>All the kids said</i>

15
00:01:11,031 --> 00:01:13,363
<i>We're way too young to die</i>

16
00:01:13,433 --> 00:01:18,234
<i>In this empty town lined with empty faces</i>

17
00:01:18,304 --> 00:01:20,499
<i>All the kids took off</i>

18
00:01:20,573 --> 00:01:23,041
<i>into this windless night</i>

19
00:01:23,109 --> 00:01:26,476
<i>Because they want to change something</i>

20
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:47,201
With this, you've woken up, right?

21
00:01:51,248 --> 00:01:53,648
We had a hindrance back then...

22
00:01:54,117 --> 00:01:55,778
but it won't be like
that this time.

23
00:01:59,156 --> 00:02:03,650
I'll show you...
the true power of Sharingan.

24
00:02:05,529 --> 00:02:09,158
Fine... Then I'll go all out too!

25
00:02:11,101 --> 00:02:15,265
You take a good look
with your Sharingan...

26
00:02:15,339 --> 00:02:17,569
at my Way of Ninja!

27
00:02:19,543 --> 00:02:21,033
Shadow Clone Jutsu!

28
00:02:24,314 --> 00:02:27,977
<i>You can't beat me by just pointlessly...</i>
<i>increasing the number!</i>

29
00:02:30,654 --> 00:02:31,586
You little!

30
00:02:38,862 --> 00:02:42,229
I can spot the real body in
one shot with my Sharingan.

31
00:02:42,733 --> 00:02:45,201
I deliberately went along
with your game...

32
00:02:48,305 --> 00:02:50,136
I won't go easy on you now!

33
00:02:57,714 --> 00:02:59,739
<i>Fire Style. Fire Ball Jutsu!</i>

34
00:03:23,507 --> 00:03:26,965
<i>Father Son.</i>
<i>The Broken Crest</i>

35
00:03:48,231 --> 00:03:52,668
<i>What was up...</i>
<i>with those eyes of Big Brother's?</i>

36
00:03:53,470 --> 00:03:57,270
<i>That wasn't...</i>
<i>just an ordinary Sharingan.</i>

37
00:04:03,113 --> 00:04:07,140
<i>And...quite a bit of time's</i>
<i>passed since then...</i>

38
00:04:07,784 --> 00:04:10,947
<i>but things are still kind of awkward</i>
<i>between him and Father.</i>

39
00:05:12,816 --> 00:05:15,808
Good morning, Father...

40
00:05:18,955 --> 00:05:21,082
Yeah, good morning.

41
00:05:22,192 --> 00:05:25,389
Sasuke... how have things
been going at the Academy lately?

42
00:05:28,799 --> 00:05:31,267
It's boring with just school classes.

43
00:05:31,802 --> 00:05:33,599
I'm always number one, so...

44
00:05:36,406 --> 00:05:38,601
Fire Style: Fire Ball Jutsu!

45
00:05:44,981 --> 00:05:45,970
<i>W-Wow...</i>

46
00:05:47,951 --> 00:05:49,919
This is the fundamental
Jutsu of the Uchiha.

47
00:05:50,854 --> 00:05:52,651
The Sign is as I taught you earlier.

48
00:05:53,290 --> 00:05:54,689
You build up Chakra,

49
00:05:54,758 --> 00:05:57,192
stop it once at around between
the mouth and the chest area,

50
00:05:57,260 --> 00:05:59,455
and spew it out at once after that.

51
00:06:00,831 --> 00:06:01,763
Try it.

52
00:06:01,832 --> 00:06:02,560
Okay!

53
00:06:05,969 --> 00:06:09,461
<i>Father...is teaching me Jutsu himself.</i>

54
00:06:10,607 --> 00:06:13,940
<i>Finally... Father has also recognized me!</i>

55
00:06:14,411 --> 00:06:15,844
<i>I must live up to his expectations!</i>

56
00:06:19,316 --> 00:06:20,647
<i>I too can...!</i>

57
00:06:22,819 --> 00:06:24,946
<i>Fire Style. Fire Ball Jutsu!</i>

58
00:06:34,998 --> 00:06:37,296
Sure enough, it won't go like
it did with Itachi, huh?

59
00:06:41,504 --> 00:06:44,166
It might've still been
too soon for you.

60
00:06:46,676 --> 00:06:48,837
<i>A member of the Uchiha Clan</i>
<i>is not recognized as full fledged</i>

61
00:06:48,912 --> 00:06:51,005
<i>until they can use the Fire Style.</i>

62
00:06:59,623 --> 00:07:01,318
<i>The Uchiha crest...</i>

63
00:07:01,391 --> 00:07:03,882
<i>means those who possess</i>
<i>the Uchiha that controls fire.</i>

64
00:07:08,999 --> 00:07:10,990
<i>Fire Style. Fire Ball Jutsu!</i>

65
00:07:14,404 --> 00:07:16,065
Damn it! One more time!

66
00:07:17,607 --> 00:07:19,575
<i>Fire Style. Fire Ball Jutsu!</i>

67
00:07:27,717 --> 00:07:29,582
<i>Fire Style. Fire Ball Jutsu!</i>

68
00:07:38,662 --> 00:07:39,788
<i>Today for sure!</i>

69
00:07:41,698 --> 00:07:43,563
<i>Fire Style. Fire Ball Jutsu!</i>

70
00:07:50,307 --> 00:07:52,366
<i>Fire Style. Fire Ball Jutsu!</i>

71
00:08:03,286 --> 00:08:04,150
Sasuke...!

72
00:08:05,288 --> 00:08:06,619
Wait a minute.

73
00:08:07,123 --> 00:08:08,147
What is it?

74
00:08:15,198 --> 00:08:16,426
What...?

75
00:08:17,133 --> 00:08:18,998
Oh... Don't move.

76
00:08:26,576 --> 00:08:28,134
Okay, finished!

77
00:08:32,716 --> 00:08:33,683
Mother...

78
00:08:33,783 --> 00:08:35,011
Hmm?

79
00:08:39,923 --> 00:08:42,619
No... It's nothing.

80
00:08:42,993 --> 00:08:43,687
Okay...

81
00:08:53,737 --> 00:08:55,728
<i>Fire Style. Fire Ball Jutsu!</i>

82
00:09:07,083 --> 00:09:09,711
<i>Sure enough, it won't go</i>
<i>like it did with Itachi, huh?</i>

83
00:09:12,589 --> 00:09:15,456
<i>It might've still been</i>
<i>too soon for you...</i>

84
00:09:16,192 --> 00:09:21,129
<i>I'm just, getting started.</i>
<i>Damn it! One more time!</i>

85
00:09:23,099 --> 00:09:25,294
<i>Fire Style. Fire Ball Jutsu!</i>

86
00:09:36,212 --> 00:09:36,871
Father!

87
00:09:37,747 --> 00:09:38,577
Hmm?

88
00:09:40,550 --> 00:09:41,608
One more time...

89
00:09:43,887 --> 00:09:46,515
One more time...
Please join me.

90
00:09:47,257 --> 00:09:49,020
It's still too soon for you.

91
00:09:49,692 --> 00:09:52,320
Even if I were to teach you
for only after a week...

92
00:09:53,563 --> 00:09:54,894
It's not that...

93
00:09:56,566 --> 00:09:58,431
I've gotten... the hang of the Jutsu.

94
00:09:59,135 --> 00:10:00,693
So I want you to see it.

95
00:10:25,428 --> 00:10:26,918
<i>Failure is not an option!</i>

96
00:10:27,363 --> 00:10:29,763
<i>Fire Style. Fire Ball Jutsu!</i>

97
00:11:22,852 --> 00:11:25,412
That's my boy.

98
00:11:28,291 --> 00:11:29,690
You've done well.

99
00:11:29,959 --> 00:11:32,985
From now on, improve yourself
and soar large

100
00:11:33,062 --> 00:11:35,963
so as not to bring shame
to the crest on your back.

101
00:11:40,637 --> 00:11:41,569
Right!

102
00:11:41,938 --> 00:11:44,668
And... let me say one thing.

103
00:11:46,709 --> 00:11:48,768
Don't chase after
your older brother anymore.

104
00:12:02,492 --> 00:12:03,686
Mother...?

105
00:12:06,296 --> 00:12:07,228
Hmm?

106
00:12:07,331 --> 00:12:12,769
What does Father really think of
Big Brother and me?

107
00:12:14,471 --> 00:12:16,496
What is it all of a sudden?

108
00:12:18,475 --> 00:12:24,641
The other day, Father said to me,
"That's my boy.

109
00:12:25,649 --> 00:12:27,776
He'd always said that only
to Big Brother.

110
00:12:28,885 --> 00:12:31,183
So I was really happy.

111
00:12:31,521 --> 00:12:33,887
I see... Good for you.

112
00:12:34,257 --> 00:12:39,354
But lately, Father and Brother
haven't been getting along, so...

113
00:12:42,666 --> 00:12:44,156
I was thinking...

114
00:12:45,469 --> 00:12:48,233
that I might just be
a replacement for Big Brother.

115
00:12:55,412 --> 00:12:58,438
Your older brother's your older brother.
And you are you.

116
00:12:58,715 --> 00:13:02,344
Your father cares deeply
about you both.

117
00:13:02,419 --> 00:13:04,717
Then why does he only think
about Big Brother?!

118
00:13:05,022 --> 00:13:07,149
That's not it...

119
00:13:07,224 --> 00:13:09,886
Your father has to protect
the Uchiha Clan

120
00:13:09,960 --> 00:13:12,554
as a representative of the clan.

121
00:13:13,063 --> 00:13:14,997
What about it?!

122
00:13:15,232 --> 00:13:18,599
Itachi is just bigger than you
and is your elder.

123
00:13:18,769 --> 00:13:20,600
He'll naturally be entrusted

124
00:13:20,671 --> 00:13:23,105
with that much more work
for the clan, right?

125
00:13:23,407 --> 00:13:26,535
Your father is the supervisor
of the work, so...

126
00:13:26,610 --> 00:13:31,013
it might be that his eyes were
likely to go towards your older brother.

127
00:13:38,021 --> 00:13:40,148
But, this is just between us.

128
00:13:41,258 --> 00:13:42,520
When he's with me,

129
00:13:42,592 --> 00:13:45,561
your father does nothing
but talk about you.

130
00:13:50,267 --> 00:13:54,363
He's just always sullen
and awkward, so...

131
00:14:12,622 --> 00:14:15,090
<i>I'll catch up to Big Brother</i>
<i>no matter what!</i>

132
00:14:31,041 --> 00:14:32,269
Damn it...!

133
00:14:37,948 --> 00:14:41,247
Big Brother's back is still
far out of reach.

134
00:14:54,197 --> 00:14:57,496
<i>Forgive me, Sasuke...</i>
<i>Maybe another time.</i>

135
00:15:00,737 --> 00:15:02,864
<i>Clan...Clan...</i>

136
00:15:03,473 --> 00:15:07,170
<i>You measure incorrectly</i>
<i>the size of your own "vessels"</i>

137
00:15:07,244 --> 00:15:12,307
<i>and don't know the depth of mine,</i>
<i>so you grovel there.</i>

138
00:15:18,255 --> 00:15:22,749
<i>My "vessel" is</i>
<i>dismayed at this foolish clan.</i>

139
00:15:23,693 --> 00:15:26,457
<i>I feel like...ever since that day,</i>

140
00:15:26,530 --> 00:15:29,522
<i>he hasn't been the same</i>
<i>as he was before.</i>

141
00:15:37,073 --> 00:15:38,335
Big Brother...

142
00:15:39,609 --> 00:15:42,544
Today, when school's finished,

143
00:15:42,612 --> 00:15:44,807
will you join me for
some Shuriken Jutsu training?

144
00:15:45,482 --> 00:15:50,010
I'm busy.
You should have Father teach you.

145
00:15:51,087 --> 00:15:57,651
But even I know that you're better
at Shuriken Jutsu than Father is.

146
00:15:58,762 --> 00:16:02,254
You always treat me like
a nuisance like that.

147
00:16:16,646 --> 00:16:20,514
Forgive me, Sasuke.
Maybe next time...

148
00:16:35,699 --> 00:16:38,065
I don't have the time to
be dealing with you today.

149
00:16:40,837 --> 00:16:45,433
You always say, "Forgive me, Sasuke,"
and poke me on the forehead.

150
00:16:45,508 --> 00:16:48,875
And you say "today,"
but it never happens.

151
00:16:52,849 --> 00:16:56,683
<i>Thank goodness...</i>
<i>he's the same as before.</i>

152
00:17:04,928 --> 00:17:06,190
<i>Big Brother...</i>

153
00:17:12,435 --> 00:17:15,427
<i>His eyes looking back</i>
<i>at Father that time...</i>

154
00:17:18,275 --> 00:17:20,641
<i>It wasn't just an ordinary Sharingan...</i>

155
00:17:22,145 --> 00:17:23,305
<i>And...</i>

156
00:17:25,448 --> 00:17:26,574
Father?

157
00:17:26,650 --> 00:17:27,617
Hmm?

158
00:17:28,118 --> 00:17:31,679
Are there several types
of Sharingan?

159
00:17:31,821 --> 00:17:36,758
Oh... You're already interested
in Sharingan?

160
00:17:37,928 --> 00:17:40,726
However, it's still too soon for you.

161
00:17:42,065 --> 00:17:44,124
It's totally different from
the Fire Style Jutsu.

162
00:17:44,334 --> 00:17:46,234
But someday, I too!

163
00:17:46,670 --> 00:17:49,764
After all... I'm your kid, so.

164
00:17:52,676 --> 00:17:56,669
Indeed, there is a Visual Jutsu
above the Sharingan,

165
00:17:56,746 --> 00:17:59,078
the Mangekyo Sharingan.

166
00:17:59,449 --> 00:18:01,679
Mangekyo Sharingan...

167
00:18:02,986 --> 00:18:05,181
In the long history of the Uchiha,

168
00:18:05,255 --> 00:18:09,624
it's a legendary Visual Jutsu
that only a few develop.

169
00:18:10,560 --> 00:18:15,964
And it's said that it only opened
under a particular condition.

170
00:18:18,668 --> 00:18:20,829
<i>A particular condition...?</i>

171
00:18:32,515 --> 00:18:34,813
<i>Don't chase after your</i>
<i>older brother anymore.</i>

172
00:18:35,752 --> 00:18:40,189
<i>I wonder what he thinks of my</i>
<i>relationship with Brother?</i>

173
00:18:42,692 --> 00:18:43,716
Father...

174
00:18:44,728 --> 00:18:48,562
Why doesn't Big Brother care
about me?

175
00:18:52,168 --> 00:18:54,295
He's a bit peculiar...

176
00:18:55,538 --> 00:18:58,974
He's a type of person who doesn't
care for making friends with people.

177
00:19:00,010 --> 00:19:01,102
Why?

178
00:19:01,745 --> 00:19:03,076
Who knows...?

179
00:19:03,947 --> 00:19:07,781
Even I, his father, can't read that boy.

180
00:19:10,587 --> 00:19:14,614
<i>Here I spoke because I wanted</i>
<i>more of Big Brother's attention.</i>

181
00:19:14,958 --> 00:19:17,552
<i>Father isn't against it.</i>

182
00:19:18,228 --> 00:19:20,788
Here, Sasuke!
Your box lunch.

183
00:19:21,398 --> 00:19:25,494
I'll watch your Shuriken practice
after you come home.

184
00:19:26,770 --> 00:19:29,466
It's not practice, it's training!

185
00:19:30,407 --> 00:19:31,738
I'm off!

186
00:19:33,877 --> 00:19:35,139
<i>That's good...</i>

187
00:19:35,612 --> 00:19:40,879
<i>It's not that Father dislikes</i>
<i>Big Brother, after all.</i>

188
00:19:43,453 --> 00:19:47,116
<i>Big Brother graduated from the Academy</i>
<i>at the top of his class at age seven.</i>

189
00:19:47,190 --> 00:19:49,658
<i>He learned to use</i>
<i>the Sharingan at age eight.</i>

190
00:19:49,726 --> 00:19:51,921
<i>And he was promoted</i>
<i>to Chunin at age ten.</i>

191
00:19:52,529 --> 00:19:56,727
<i>But, I've got the same Uchiha blood</i>
<i>flowing inside me as he does.</i>

192
00:19:57,100 --> 00:19:58,795
<i>I won't lose to him!</i>

193
00:20:09,779 --> 00:20:13,647
You're not gonna tell me this is
the best you can do, are you?

194
00:20:14,484 --> 00:20:17,817
You boast about your Way of Ninja
and this is all you've got?

195
00:20:22,692 --> 00:20:25,991
Are you still thinking that
I'm a member of your comrade game?

196
00:20:29,099 --> 00:20:31,158
If that's the case, you're...

197
00:20:31,835 --> 00:20:33,860
a hopeless fool!

198
00:20:37,073 --> 00:20:38,472
Stop wasting time!

199
00:20:39,042 --> 00:20:40,634
Give me all you've got,

200
00:20:40,710 --> 00:20:43,201
you number one hyperactive,
knucklehead Ninja!

201
00:21:12,208 --> 00:21:17,043
<i>When I recalled the parts one by one,</i>

202
00:21:17,113 --> 00:21:23,416
<i>I felt as though</i>
<i>I had understood everything</i>

203
00:21:23,486 --> 00:21:33,987
<i>Faded words which I kept so close to me</i>

204
00:21:34,297 --> 00:21:43,763
<i>Speechless nights, a hint of warmth,</i>

205
00:21:45,508 --> 00:21:50,502
<i>and this distant yearning for you</i>

206
00:21:50,813 --> 00:21:59,812
<i>I live, simply repeating this cycle</i>

207
00:22:01,991 --> 00:22:11,525
<i>Held in my two hands</i>
<i>A droplet of time</i>

208
00:22:12,969 --> 00:22:21,968
<i>Softly clutching forgotten memories</i>
<i>Lost words</i>

209
00:22:30,853 --> 00:22:34,721
<i>I'll keep these thoughts...</i>

210
00:22:38,962 --> 00:22:40,486
Just as Neji said,

211
00:22:40,563 --> 00:22:43,157
it seems Sasuke's in
the darkness right now.

212
00:22:43,433 --> 00:22:44,593
Damn it.

213
00:22:44,867 --> 00:22:46,767
He really did hit me with
all his might.

214
00:22:47,437 --> 00:22:52,568
Hey Sasuke, am I not your comrade
or anything anymore?!

215
00:22:52,809 --> 00:22:56,870
Don't all those things we
did together in Squad Seven

216
00:22:56,946 --> 00:22:59,506
mean anything to you?!

217
00:22:59,916 --> 00:23:03,181
Next episode,
"The Secrets of the Mangekyo Sharingan!
